=head1 DESCRIPTION

The policy directives and their values that CloudFront includes as
values for the C<Content-Security-Policy> HTTP response header.

For more information about the C<Content-Security-Policy> HTTP response
header, see Content-Security-Policy
(https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy)
in the MDN Web Docs.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ContentSecurityPolicy => Str

The policy directives and their values that CloudFront includes as
values for the C<Content-Security-Policy> HTTP response header.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Override => Bool

A Boolean that determines whether CloudFront overrides the
C<Content-Security-Policy> HTTP response header received from the
origin with the one specified in this response headers policy.



